000>(2/7/01 9:30:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Hey everyone I just hit my third hell level, and was wondering where I should go to hunt that will give me the best experience possible.  Any comments will be appreciated.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uerykaeq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ErykaEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/01 10:02:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Sol B /nod<br>
You'll be out of 40 in no time.<br>
<br>
Eryka<br>
DE Warrior of Lanys <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ulyriel2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lyriel2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/01 11:16:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Sol B, CoM, Overthere, WW...lot's of places <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><html>
