</html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukobodaishi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kobodaishi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/28/01 1:24:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Give Kobo a goblin... plaguebringer, whipcracker, slinger, mosstrooper, cavehunter, or what have you, and Kobo will bash, slash, and pierce them to pieces. One yellow/orange bubble per hour in Droga. 35-40 Enchanter, Druid, Secondary Warrior, and Bard is all you need.<br>
<br>
Kobodaishi Sama<br>
40 War Karana<br>
Silver Daggers <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwandork.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/28/01 2:51:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> You may want to try the north wall in DL. Loot sucks, scenery is boring, but you can constant pull for hours on end. Getting a group is ez for tanks here, there are never enough to go around. You can rake in exp here into the late 40s. If you get bored, at 45 you can start getting into groups in KC. A balanced group of 45-50 can hold captain camp pretty easily so you can get your jade mace. If you are after non stop killng and exp - DL is the place to be. <p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-famliy: arial"><b>Wandor Kilbringer<br>Wizard of the 45th Conclave<br>Vini, Vidi, Nuki</b></span><br>
<i>I came, I saw, I nuked the crap out of everything in sight!</i><p>
<span style="font-size: 14px; font-famliy: arial"><b>Moordian Killbringer<br>Warrior of 22 Battle Scars</b><br><i>Dwarven LaMachine of Death</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uimlaq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Imlaq</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/30/01 10:51:23 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Another vote for Sol B - did most of 40 in one session in KPC on Saturday.  Everyone got loot - RMBs for the clerics and a Carnal Pauldron and Painbringer (nice name, forget the rest *grin*) for me. <p><font color="antiquewhite">Imlaq Machinshin</font><BR>
<font color="antiquewhite">Dragoon 41st Legion</font><BR><BR>
"Death is light as a feather, Duty heavy as a mountain"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugoofeeiimikmunkymon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goofeeii MikMunkymon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.skorchers.com/revive/members/pics/goof10x10.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/30/01 1:18:17 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.skorchers.com/revive/members/pics/goofeeii60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> Depends on your race...sort of...<br>
If your a big race, Sol B is gonna be a pain...shrink potions are hard to find cheap, and there aren't many shamans in there...(from my experience)<br>
<br>
Go to Lower Guk (Great Loot too) or Dreadlands...<br>
<br>
Dreadlands is the easiest to find a group...<br>
You also might want to try Eastern Wastes...but I hate velious...Its not really a place to group, more of a continent scaled towards guild raids, etc. <p><center><img src="http://www.skorchers.com/revive/members/pics/goofsig60.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ugreblaja.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Greblaja</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 116<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/31/01 4:56:41 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hunting at 40??</span><hr size=1> LGuk is old school, but still very nice for 37-50,51 <p>-G<P>
